article_title: Congressman to Sebelius: 'It's like talking to the Republic of Korea'

article_metadata.description: Video on NBCNews.com: Rep. John Shimkus, R-Ill., and U.S. Secretary of Health and Human Services Kathleen Sebelius discuss the implementation of the Affordable Care Act Wednesday on Capitol Hill.
